full diff, full bad, full order, full money from Tir to Avalon.<br>
<br>
Kasnohazet, 40 MA. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uhurtyouao.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hurtyou AO</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Peking Duck</span><br>  Posts: 127<br> <font color=#660000>(9/20/01 3:50:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> If you have a Yalmaha..</span><hr size=1> You can do another fun Route. Avalon-Southern foul hills. <br>
<br>
At 79 they pay about 90k each on 60% difficulty. To get there you grid to omni entertainment,  exit through east gate and then continue east through Omni Forest. <br>
<br>
The good part is that the mission areas are usually quite small (like Aegen).<br>
<br>
